94
00:04:42,496 --> 00:04:45,579
And if the game is in an imbalanced state for too long,

95
00:04:45,819 --> 00:04:47,921
that kind of suggests to the players that we don't care.

96
00:04:48,382 --> 00:04:50,123
And so it's kind of violating, you know,

97
00:04:50,604 --> 00:04:52,566
trying to hold up player trust as being so important.

