Pros can do amazing things that we mere mortals cannot possibly conceive of doing.

106
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,983
And balance at high skill level, and especially at pro skill level,

107
00:05:28,303 --> 00:05:30,905
is really different from balance for the rest of the game,

108
00:05:30,925 --> 00:05:32,086
and certainly for newer players.

