00:11:03,528 --> 00:11:06,091
So here is Heimerdinger from League of Legends, Torbjorn

203
00:11:06,131 --> 00:11:08,673
from Overwatch, and the engineer from Team Fortress.

204
00:11:09,963 --> 00:11:13,847
The problem with AI power, in this case the turrets, but it also could be like

205
00:11:14,387 --> 00:11:15,528
your character has a pet.

206
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:19,192
