00:25:58,645 --> 00:26:02,648
have three days to decide something's amiss, make

484
00:26:02,709 --> 00:26:05,671
changes, test those changes, make additional changes, and

485
00:26:05,711 --> 00:26:06,752
then get it out there to players.

486
00:26:10,035 --> 00:26:12,297
Our live team is backed up by a play test team of very

487
00:26:12,337 --> 00:26:12,978
skilled players.

488
00:26:13,078 --> 00:26:14,659
Many of these players are ex-pros.

489
00:26:16,169 --> 00:26:19,231
The playtest team is critical for us to get early impressions and data.

490
00:26:19,531 --> 00:26:23,894
You can think of it as being able to deploy your patch early or having a beta even before your beta.

491
00:26:25,708 --> 00:26:27,508
I've been able to create a playtest team at all three

492
00:26:27,548 --> 00:26:30,189
studios where I've worked, at Ensemble, Blizzard,

493
00:26:30,289 --> 00:26:31,009
and now at Riot.

