00:27:38,618 --> 00:27:40,019
Her win rate did not hit our targets.

522
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:46,352
We know these changes are going to compromise balance and disrupt the game for players.

523
00:27:48,113 --> 00:27:52,395
This past preseason we made a massive change to the assassin characters in League of Legends.

524
00:27:52,655 --> 00:27:56,617
This not only involved individual champions, but their items, their masteries.

525
00:27:56,637 --> 00:28:01,439
We even changed the way stealth works, since stealth is really tied into assassin characters.

526
00:28:03,775 --> 00:28:07,457
And again, we do this deliberately, make these kind of disruptive changes knowing that it's worth it,

527
00:28:07,637 --> 00:28:09,318
but also knowing that balance will take a hit.

528
00:28:09,859 --> 00:28:12,020
And during these times, players are going to say,

529
00:28:12,841 --> 00:28:15,402
WTF, Riot? Why is your balance team asleep at the wheel?

530
00:28:15,902 --> 00:28:20,145
When really, we've made life hard on the balance team by making all these other changes to the game.

531
00:28:21,246 --> 00:28:25,148
So we try to constrain the most disruptive changes to pre-season and mid-season.

532
00:28:26,306 --> 00:28:30,232
Messaging here is super important so the players understand what's going on and understand that,

533
00:28:30,572 --> 00:28:33,957
hey guys, things will be a little crazy for a while, we're putting plants in the game,

534
00:28:34,177 --> 00:28:35,860
we're trying a new pick-ban system, whatever.

535
00:28:36,681 --> 00:28:38,604
We know that's going to come at a balanced cost,

536
00:28:38,784 --> 00:28:41,789
and because we patch quickly, we're going to try to get things back to a stable place.

537
00:28:47,326 --> 00:28:49,626
Now, I have a few slides here on using data.

538
00:28:50,167 --> 00:28:51,907
We gather a lot of data, right?

