00:28:51,987 --> 00:28:54,007
It has a really powerful insights team,

540
00:28:54,327 --> 00:28:56,068
and they help us to collect a lot of analytics

541
00:28:56,108 --> 00:28:58,608
about the game, and then help us to interpret that as well.

542
00:29:01,349 --> 00:29:02,749
I know I talk about win rate a lot.

543
00:29:02,909 --> 00:29:04,189
That is an important stat for us.

