00:29:25,832 --> 00:29:26,973
So here's an example of win rate.

552
00:29:27,013 --> 00:29:28,594
But we're looking at win rate by skill level.

553
00:29:28,934 --> 00:29:32,738
So on the left of each of these curves is the bronze

554
00:29:32,798 --> 00:29:34,099
players, and at the right is kind of

555
00:29:34,159 --> 00:29:35,160
challenger master tier.

556
00:29:36,460 --> 00:29:39,742
You can see a character, a champion like Veigar, hovers at around a 50% win rate.

