00:30:34,249 --> 00:30:35,270
Similarly, here are

572
00:30:37,017 --> 00:30:39,678
the number of games on a champion, irrespective of ELO.

573
00:30:40,218 --> 00:30:42,619
You can see a character here like Aurelion Sol.

574
00:30:43,119 --> 00:30:45,560
Your first game of Aurelion Sol, you may lose.

575
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:48,321
In fact, you may lose a lot of games with Aurelion Sol

