00:30:57,824 --> 00:30:58,804
On the other end of the spectrum

581
00:30:58,904 --> 00:31:00,245
is a champion named Volibear.

582
00:31:01,165 --> 00:31:02,786
After you've played Volibear two or three times,

583
00:31:02,806 --> 00:31:05,046
you've probably seen about all that Volibear has to offer.

